We have made significant progress in the Webhooks and Integrations area. We have
added and improved several integrations, including but not limited to:

1. Beeminder
2. Front
3. Dialogflow
4. Flock
5. Dropbox

We have also added a reminder bot and slash commands to trigger reminders on
individual messages. {insert doc link here}. There are minor refinements in the
interface for creating bots and consistency in how the bot profiles are visible
in the user interface.

